Class SavingsAccountTransaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.data.jpa.domain.AbstractPersistable<java.lang.Long>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    @Entity
public final class SavingsAccountTransaction
extends org.springframework.data.jpa.domain.AbstractPersistable<java.lang.Long>
    All monetary transactions against a savings account are modelled through this entity.
